      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. but if they're working together like that, why would the rise be so unpredictable? is it possible for one to get ahead of the other? like, could the bacteria be slowing down the yeast, or is there something else about how these microscopic organisms behave in the mixture that causes it to be so temperamental?",
