      "role": "user",
      "content": "it feels like something is just acting a bit chaotic in there, like they're not following a predictable pattern. since they're basically invisible and just living in there, is there any way to actually observe the health of the colony or see if one group is starting to outcompete the other before it actually ruins the dough?",
